# Cloudflare Pages — security headers applied to every response.
#
# CSP notes:
# - script-src is 'self' (NO 'unsafe-inline') — every page's JS now lives in its own file
#   (S9: homepage -> /assets/home.js, admin -> /assets/admin.js, changelog ->
#   /assets/changelog.js; the app pages already load external scripts). So an injected
#   inline <script> or onX= handler will not execute, even if markup escaping ever slips.
# - style-src is 'self' (NO 'unsafe-inline') — S18/A55 is DONE. There is no inline <style> block
#   and no style="" attribute on any served page: the marketing/admin pages' static inline CSS was
#   extracted to linked stylesheets (home.css, admin.css, site.css), and every dynamic style on the
#   Svelte surfaces is now applied via the CSSOM (NOT gated by style-src): the chart swatch/bar
#   colors+widths go through a use:styleProps action that calls element.style.setProperty(), and the
#   export-report iframe injects its CSS via a constructable stylesheet (adoptedStyleSheets) instead
#   of an inline <style>. Vite extracts every Svelte component <style> to a linked .css at build, so
#   the bundled output carries no inline style either. Result: an injected inline <style> or style=""
#   will not apply, hardening against CSS-based exfiltration/UI-redress. (script-src already omits
#   'unsafe-inline', so this is defense-in-depth, not the only line.)
# - No external origins are needed: every fetch is same-origin (/api/*, /data/*, /app/),
#   and per-trade screenshots are data: URLs (hence img-src 'self' data:). No 'unsafe-eval'.
# - When Stripe checkout lands it redirects (full navigation), so no CSP change is needed;
#   embedded Stripe would need frame-src.

/*
  X-Frame-Options: DENY
  X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff
  Referrer-Policy: strict-origin-when-cross-origin
  Permissions-Policy: camera=(), microphone=(), geolocation=(), browsing-topics=()
  Content-Security-Policy: default-src 'self'; script-src 'self'; style-src 'self'; img-src 'self' data:; font-src 'self'; connect-src 'self'; object-src 'none'; base-uri 'self'; form-action 'self'; frame-ancestors 'none'
